{
  "stem": "15962.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we could only play with other Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I meant, at, at first during the occupation, we would visit each other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I think slowly, most Christians were afraid to meet Jews and did in a clandestine way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there were many courageous people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And some of them also hid valuable things for my parents, such as cameras and watches and--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hid them for them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is how even the family album was saved and some of the valuable papers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Birth certificates and so on that I have today were with a bank clerk over-- during the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they, they returned them to me voluntarily after the war, even though I had no clue that they had any of our objects.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After the war?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody has-- of the immediate family-- has perished until then.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was really the beginning of the deportation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the 15th of December, 1942, we all had to assemble at the local railway station and were sent to the county seat, where we stayed in the high school for one or two nights.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Jews were taken there from the whole county and then shipped by train to Theres-- to the ghetto of Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These were kind of normal passenger trains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was still fairly humane.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were limited to something like two large suitcases at that time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the limit really was also that at that time, the train station to Theresienstadt stopped in a town about five or 10 kilometers from Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody had to walk there and carry their luggage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that was a little also a limiting factor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Obviously, they were-- I know that there were several families who took their lives the night before the deportation.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there was definitely apprehension.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
